{
  "texts": [
    "The exponential growth in interest in AI-related topics after February 2022 indicates a shifting trend.",
    "AI in marketing must consider the target audience's mental state (Mariani et al., 2021).",
    "That is why AI content must take social and ethical concerns into account.",
    "AI is helping marketers make sense of the vast amounts of user data and cryptic user intent to navigate the ever-changing landscape of content marketing.",
    "Short tales, such as stock market reports and sports scores, may soon be automatically generated by AI to save time for marketers."
  ]
}